Module it.polimi.ingsw.gc19
Package it.polimi.ingsw.gc19.View.GameLocalView

Class LocalTable

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.gc19.View.GameLocalView.LocalTable
public class LocalTable extends Object
The class contains the table that the Client can access to pick card or be represented by its view. It is created by the LocalModel class.
